Package: wikiISO31662
Type: Package
Title: Provides ISO 3166-2 Subdivision and Country Codes According to Wikipedia
Version: 0.1.3
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jarrett",
           family = "Byrnes",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jarrett.byrnes@umb.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9791-9472"))
Description: This package provides a table of ISO 3166-2 codes for subdivisions as scraped from Wikipedia via <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_3166-2> for easy use in matching names to ISO codes. The data provided has many variations of names in different languages to ease difficult string matching tasks.
